<div id="review_2901411465" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2901411465" />
    <a title="John Wood" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9352033-john-wood"><img alt="John Wood" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1337464454p2/9352033.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2901411465?book_show_action=true">Sep 29, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="John Wood" class="user" itemprop="url" name="John Wood" href="/user/show/9352033-john-wood">John Wood</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2901411465" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10148149506372716569">Sixteen essays by James M. McPherson, a leading historian of the American Civil War. Very readable, very interesting, covering a great variety of topics, full of insights and clarifications. Of course, it is well researched and documented. A must-read for any Civil war buff.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


